## Code Standards

-  Indentation: 2 spaces (not tabs)
-  Encoding: UTF-8
-  Line endings: LF (Unix)
-  Trailing whitespace: Remove
-  Final newline: Always add

## Markdown Standards

-  ALWAYS add blank line after headers (###, ##, #)
-  Use 2 spaces after list markers (MD030)
-  Lists must be surrounded by blank lines (MD032)
-  Always specify language in code blocks (MD040)

